        <updateDate>2009-04-03T20:25:18Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ Freedom From Unnecessary Litigation Act of 2009 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) allow a tax credit for insurance purchased to cover the costs of a negative outcome from surgery, including negative outcomes caused by physician malpractice; and (2) exclude from gross income medical malpractice awards granted in binding arbitration.]]></text>
      </summary>
